``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} airbnb <- airbnb %>% drop_na() ``` ::: ## Time Dependent Visualization ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} airbnb %>% ggplot(aes(last_review, fill = neighbourhood_group)) + geom_density(alpha = 0.9, adjust = 5) + facet_wrap(vars(neighbourhood_group)) + theme_minimal() + labs(title = "Last Review dates of different neighbourhood groups") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](challenge6_ManiShankerKamarapu_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-5-1.png){width=672} ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} airbnb %>% ggplot(aes(last_review, fill = room_type)) + geom_density(alpha=0.9) + facet_wrap(vars(room_type)) + theme_minimal() + labs(title = "Last Review dates of different rooms") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](challenge6_ManiShankerKamarapu_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-6-1.png){width=672} ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} airbnb %>% ggplot(aes(last_review, number_of_reviews)) + geom_line() + theme_minimal() + labs(title = "Last review date of AB_NYC_2019") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](challenge6_ManiShankerKamarapu_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-7-1.png){width=672} ::: ::: ## Visualizing Part-Whole Relationships ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} airbnb %>% ggplot(aes(last_review, price, color = room_type)) + geom_point(size = .5) + geom_line() + theme_minimal() + labs(title = "Price in differnt years according to room types") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](challenge6_ManiShankerKamarapu_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-8-1.png){width=672} ::: ```{.r .cell-code} airbnb %>% ggplot(aes(last_review, price, color = neighbourhood_group)) + geom_point(size = .5) + geom_line() + theme_minimal() + labs(title = "Price in different years according to neighbourhood groups") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](challenge6_ManiShankerKamarapu_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-8-2.png){width=672} ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} airbnb %>% ggplot(aes(room_type, price, color = room_type)) + geom_point() + theme_minimal() + facet_wrap(vars(neighbourhood_group)) + theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90,hjust = 1)) + labs(title = "Price in different rooms according to neighbourhood groups") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](challenge6_ManiShankerKamarapu_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-9-1.png){width=672} ::: :::
